msgid "This utility should only be used in live mode!"
msgstr "This utility should only be used in live mode!"

msgid ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the "
"Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting "
"correctly there are no problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux "
"distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the "
"Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting "
"correctly there are no problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux "
"distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"

msgid "Restore Boot, Grub and Initrd"
msgstr "Restore Boot, Grub and Initrd"

msgid "Wait..."
msgstr "Wait..."

msgid "I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"
msgstr ""
"I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"

msgid ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't "
"find any EFI partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS "
"mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't "
"find any EFI partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS "
"mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"

msgid ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this "
"computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this "
"computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"

msgid "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."
msgstr "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."

msgid "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "
msgstr "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one "
"should restore the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one "
